nós a mudar o mundo juntos.

394
00:24:45,257 --> 00:24:49,234
E a beber tanto café!

395
00:24:51,317 --> 00:24:56,281
Tracy Brand.
Dás-me a honra

396
00:24:56,282 --> 00:24:59,216
